  <brief_title>Comparison of Hemi-shoulder Arthroplasty and PHILOS in Treating Three or Four-part Fractures of Proximal Humerus</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Multi-center Study on Comparison of Hemi-shoulder Arthroplasty and PHILOS in Treating Three or Four-part Fractures of Proximal Humerus.</official_title>
